{"tid":2307842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麥美娟批警司警誡決定屬「心軟」容海恩擔心簽保守行為對年輕人未必有警惕性 李家超：大前題係要認錯","createTime":"2020-12-01T12:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T00:40:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2981480159be3db10af096edb280aca4bcf4a0","tid":2307842,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"立法會保安事務委員會今舉行政策簡報會。工聯會麥美娟提到林鄭早前形容李家超是「心太軟」，質問當局提出警司警誡決定是「局長你心軟」，「定係計劃咩目的呢？」她又稱，不少人擔心「愛你變成害你」，令年輕人成為犯法的工具。<br />\n<br />\n麥又指，有執法人員被起底，受到「白色恐怖」，要求當局正視，並與私隱專員公署商討修例，進一步保障執法人員。<br />\n<br />\n新民黨容海恩擔心當局就簽保守行為以2年為限，對年輕人未必有警惕性，建議當局可延長守行為的時間。<br />\n<br />\n李家超強調，考慮警司警誡和守行為時，只限輕微罪行。他又指，一些青少年是在其他人壓力下參與，應情有可原，但大前題是承認自己犯錯。他又稱，對涉案者在認識歷史上亦會「做啲工夫」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/A377GFGNHZDQBCCVQF2SOK4ANU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FA377GFGNHZDQBCCVQF2SOK4ANU%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0oL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=38b95b6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FA377GFGNHZDQBCCVQF2SOK4ANU%2F&h=391998a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/A377GFGNHZDQBCCVQF2SOK4ANU/</a>"},{"pid":"9fdc0d218dd4866b995b82c7dd332af07d4efbf0","tid":2307842,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"好想嘔"},{"pid":"3ebf5a91e2826cabe201987ee4da8d29ed7ea2a3","tid":2307842,"uid":264245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"無做過點解要認呀屌你老母<br />\n成班假證狗"},{"pid":"57984982c7fbb7d425e96b0604bc6e03ab72a219","tid":2307842,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60eef73680ef8a07d49484d16ce1bcc45d24c55","tid":2307842,"uid":3873,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202